NAPLES, Fla. - Participate in a live chat with Naples Daily News journalists and area gridiron fans during Week 9 of high school football action in Southwest Florida. 
Here is a schedule of tonight's games: Palmetto Ridge 16, Gulf Coast 10, halftime Community School 41, Marco Island Academy 13, halftime First Baptist 52, St. John Neumann 0, halftime Immokalee 13, Dunbar 7, 3rd Lely 20, Cypress Lake 0, 3rd Naples 21, South Fort Myers 20, 2nd 
Share your photos with us: Each week fans can submit their photos for a chance to win a large pizza & T-shirt from Il Primo Pizza and Wings. Post game pics to Instagram or Twitter and use #NDNPrepZone for a chance to win. A winner will be selected every Tuesday.
